ingredients: 3 cups cooked elbow macaroni or corkscrew-shaped pasta
2 (5 ounce) cans Swanson® Premium Chunk Chicken Breast in Water, drained
1 small cucumber, cut in half lengthwise and sliced
1 1/2 cups cherry tomatoes, cut in half
3/4 cup prepared fat-free Italian salad dressing
title: Cool Chicken 'n' Pasta Salad
instructions: In large bowl toss macaroni, chicken, cucumber, tomatoes, onion, parsley and dressing until evenly coated. Refrigerate at least 30 minutes.
